@node Carpets
@subsection Carpets
@cindex carpets

@dfn{Carpets}@footnote{@dfn{Carpets} are called @emph{tapestry} in the
original game.} are ornamental constructions often placed over
@code{DOOR} cons.  They come in two flavors: @code{CARPET} and
