6@arrow{}@code{FAT_GUARD}, 12@arrow{}@code{SHADOW},
13@arrow{}@code{VIZIER}, others@arrow@code{GUARD}.} while the latter
determines only his coloring.  The five guard types are: @code{GUARD},
